        title: "Servicios para extranjeros",
        text: "Acompanamos compras y tramites cuando el cliente opera desde fuera o necesita documentacion internacional.",
        points: [
          "Obtencion de NIE",
          "Revision de documentacion internacional",
          "Asistencia en compras desde el extranjero",
        ],
      },
    ],
    closingTitle: "Servicios legales pensados para ordenar la operacion y reducir riesgo",
    closingIntro:
      "Te acompanamos en la compra, venta o alquiler con revision legal previa, coordinacion documental y representacion si la operacion necesita defensa posterior.",
    closingPrimary: "Solicitar asesoria legal",
    closingSecondary: "Ver comercializacion",
  },
  en: {
    title: "Legal services | BlancaReal",
    description:
      "Real estate legal services on the Costa del Sol for contracts, due diligence, tax advice, documentation, representation and support for foreign buyers, sellers and landlords.",
    eyebrow: "Legal services",
    headingMain: "Real estate legal services on the Costa del Sol",
    headingSub: "Contracts, due diligence, tax advice, documentation, representation and international support",
    intro:
      "We tailor legal support to each property transaction: purchase, sale, rental, regularization, notary signing and formal representation if the matter later becomes contentious.",
    primaryCta: "Talk to legal team",
    secondaryCta: "Go to contact",
    heroStats: [
      { value: "6 areas", label: "of real estate legal coverage" },
      { value: "Costa del Sol", label: "purchase, sale, rental and investment" },
      { value: "National and international clients", label: "end-to-end legal support" },
    ],
    deskEyebrow: "Legal desk",
    deskTitle: "We step in where legal risk begins in the asset and in the transaction.",
    deskText:
      "Our legal work covers document preparation, registry and planning review, tax implications, transaction formalities and representation whenever a dispute affects the property or the agreement.",
    deskTags: ["Contracts", "Due diligence", "Tax", "Notary", "Representation", "NIE"],
    sections: {
      coverageEyebrow: "Coverage",
      coverageHeading: "Legal services we provide within a real estate transaction",
      coverageIntro:
        "The page is structured around clear service areas so clients understand exactly what we review, prepare, coordinate or defend in each transaction or dispute.",
    },
    coverage: [
      {
        id: "contracts",
        label: "01",
        title: "Contract drafting and review",
        text: "We prepare and review the contractual base of the transaction so each party signs with clearer terms and lower exposure.",
